data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of style and comfort at 712 Burlington Ln. This charming 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is located in Warrensburg. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a welcoming atmosphere, with brand new carpet throughout and new grouted vinyl in the bathrooms, kitchen, and dining area.

One of the standout features of this home is the full finished basement, providing you with ample room for a wide range of possibilities – a home office, a game room, or a cozy retreat for movie nights. The possibilities are endless.

The exterior of the home has been meticulously landscaped, offering an inviting curb appeal that you'll be proud to call your own. Enjoy hosting or enjoying mild Fall nights on the new composite deck off the kitchen! The home also boasts new fans for efficient cooling and a new shower door and a new water heater in 2017.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today!
